  provinceImage3: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 0851ad847470a464ab5ef3298be59e12, type: 3}
  description: "Tuy\xEAn Quang l\xE0 m\u1ED9t t\u1EC9nh thu\u1ED9c v\xF9ng Trung
    du v\xE0 mi\u1EC1n n\xFAi B\u1EAFc B\u1ED9 \u1EDF ph\xEDa B\u1EAFc c\u1EE7a Vi\u1EC7t
    Nam. Trung t\xE2m c\u1EE7a t\u1EC9nh l\xE0 th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 Tuy\xEAn Quang.
    T\u1EC9nh c\xF3 \u0111\u1ECBa h\xECnh ch\u1EE7 y\u1EBFu l\xE0 \u0111\u1ED3i n\xFAi
    v\xE0 r\u1EEBng t\u1EF1 nhi\xEAn, v\u1EDBi nhi\u1EC1u \u0111\u1ECBa danh n\u1ED5i
    b\u1EADt nh\u01B0 Khu di t\xEDch qu\u1ED1c gia \u0111\u1EB7c bi\u1EC7t T\xE2n
    Tr\xE0o \u2013 n\u01A1i g\u1EAFn li\u1EC1n v\u1EDBi nhi\u1EC1u s\u1EF1 ki\u1EC7n
    quan tr\u1ECDng c\u1EE7a c\xE1ch m\u1EA1ng Vi\u1EC7t Nam, v\xE0 H\u1ED3 Na Hang
    v\u1EDBi c\u1EA3nh quan thi\xEAn nhi\xEAn h\xF9ng v\u0129.\n\nTuy\xEAn Quang
    c\xF3 nhi\u1EC1u \u0111\u1EB7c s\u1EA3n \u0111\u1ECBa ph\u01B0\u01A1ng nh\u01B0
    Cam s\xE0nh H\xE0m Y\xEAn, B\xE1nh gai Chi\xEAm H\xF3a v\xE0 c\xE1c s\u1EA3n
    ph\u1EA9m t\u1EEB n\xF4ng s\u1EA3n v\xF9ng n\xFAi.\n\nV\u1EC1 v\u0103n h\xF3a,
    Tuy\xEAn Quang l\xE0 n\u01A1i sinh s\u1ED1ng c\u1EE7a nhi\u1EC1u d\xE2n t\u1ED9c
    nh\u01B0 T\xE0y, Dao, S\xE1n D\xECu v\u1EDBi b\u1EA3n s\u1EAFc v\u0103n h\xF3a
    phong ph\xFA. M\u1ED9t n\xE9t v\u0103n h\xF3a \u0111\u1EB7c s\u1EAFc c\u1EE7a
    \u0111\u1ECBa ph\u01B0\u01A1ng l\xE0 L\u1EC5 h\u1ED9i Th\xE0nh Tuy\xEAn, n\u1ED5i
    ti\u1EBFng v\u1EDBi nh\u1EEFng m\xF4 h\xECnh \u0111\xE8n l\u1ED3ng l\u1EDBn v\xE0
    ho\u1EA1t \u0111\u1ED9ng v\u0103n h\xF3a thu h\xFAt \u0111\xF4ng \u0111\u1EA3o
    du kh\xE1ch."
  desSatNhap: "Tuy\xEAn Quang sau s\xE1p nh\u1EADp 2025 (Tuy\xEAn Quang + H\xE0 Giang):
    th\xE0nh ph\u1EA7n, trung t\xE2m h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh, di\u1EC7n t\xEDch\u2013d\xE2n
    s\u1ED1, danh s\xE1ch huy\u1EC7n/x\xE3, h\u1EA1 t\u1EA7ng, c\u01A1 h\u1ED9i B\u0110S.
    T\u1EEB 12/06/2025, h\u1EE3p nh\u1EA5t t\u1EC9nh Tuy\xEAn Quang v\xE0 t\u1EC9nh
    H\xE0 Giang th\xE0nh \u0111\u01A1n v\u1ECB c\u1EA5p t\u1EC9nh m\u1EDBi mang t\xEAn
    Tuy\xEAn Quang, trung t\xE2m h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh \u0111\u1EB7t t\u1EA1i Tuy\xEAn
    Quang."
